<p>When the market is highly volatile, the price of BNB can experience rapid changes, which can affect the value of your staked assets and ultimately impact the rewards you earn. It&#8217;s important to consider this risk when participating in staking pools and to implement risk management strategies to mitigate potential losses.</p>



