<p>Binance Academy emphasizes the flexibility of staking BNB. Delegated staking allows you to earn rewards immediately while maintaining some liquidity, as you can often withdraw your stake with minimal delay. Here&#8217;s a quick comparison:</p>



<figure class="wp-block-table"><table><thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>Staking Pools</th><th>Delegated Staking</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Liquidity</td><td>Lower</td><td>Higher</td></tr><tr><td>Reward Potential</td><td>Higher</td><td>Varies</td></tr><tr><td>Access</td><td>Binance account required</td><td>Binance account required</td></tr><tr><td>Flexibility</td><td>Fixed terms</td><td>Flexible terms</td></tr><tr><td>Support</td><td>Binance supports staking</td><td>Binance supports staking</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>



